OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,FThe Chair of Manx Care is the latest
OL,7,Fsenior official to announce she will
OL,8,Fbe stepping down from her role.
OL,10,FProfessor Wendy Reid has been the
OL,11,FChair of the Isle of Man's health
OL,12,Fservice since February 2024, but says
OL,13,Fit is time for Manx Care to move into
OL,14,Fthe "next phase" of leadership.
OL,16,FHer announcement comes just a week
OL,17,Fafter the service's Chief Executive,
OL,18,FTeresa Cope, confirmed she would be
OL,19,Fstanding down and leaving the
OL,20,Forganisation in the summer of 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779304271
OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,FProfessor Reid said: "It has been a
OL,7,Fprivilege to chair the organisation
OL,8,Ffor more than two years and I am
OL,9,Fimmensely proud of what has been
OL,10,Fachieved during that time. This
OL,11,Fincludes delivering important clinical
OL,12,Fimprovements, strengthened governance
OL,13,Fand the continued development of
OL,14,Fsocial care services in the Island.
OL,16,F"I have also worked hard to strengthen
OL,17,Fthe board through the recruitment of
OL,18,Flocal non-executive directors and,
OL,19,Fdespite some delays, these
OL,20,Fappointments are now in post."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779304271
OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,FHer departure means Manx Care will
OL,7,Flose both its Chair and Chief
OL,8,FExecutive within months of each other
OL,9,Fduring a difficult period for the
OL,10,Fhealth service.
OL,12,FIn early May 2026, Manx Care faced
OL,13,F"extreme pressures", with patients
OL,14,Fwaiting over 12 hours in the Emergency
OL,15,FDepartment, causing the health service
OL,16,Fto escalate to the highest alert level
OL,17,Ffor operational pressure.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779304271
OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,FManx Care says the strain on services
OL,7,Fhas now eased, but the organisation is
OL,8,Ffacing a Governance Review after
OL,9,Fclinicians raised concerns over how it
OL,10,Fis being run.
OL,12,FProfessor Reid added: "Health and
OL,13,Fsocial care services continue to face
OL,14,Fsignificant pressures, particularly
OL,15,Frising demand and increasing
OL,16,Fcomplexity of care. These pressures
OL,17,Fmean accepting uncomfortable trade-
OL,18,Foffs or risk instability when
OL,19,Fexpectations exceed capacity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779304271
OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,F"I came to the Island to work
OL,7,Falongside Teresa Cope (Chief
OL,8,FExecutive) and, following Teresa's
OL,9,Fdecision to move on at the end of next
OL,10,Fmonth, I believe it is also the right
OL,11,Ftime for me to do the same.
OL,13,F"With the Department of Health and
OL,14,FSocial Care progressing its Governance
OL,15,FReview, this is an appropriate moment
OL,16,Fto allow the next phase of leadership
OL,17,Fand governance arrangements to be
OL,18,Fshaped for the future."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779304271
OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,F"However, I have every confidence in
OL,7,Fthe professionalism and dedication of
OL,8,Fthe teams across Manx Care to continue
OL,9,Fdelivering high-quality care for our
OL,10,Fcommunity. I want to thank them
OL,11,Fpersonally for their daily efforts and
OL,12,Ftheir expertise."
OL,14,FThe announcement comes on the same day
OL,15,Fas the Isle of Man's Parliament was
OL,16,Fasked to approve #20.8m in additional
OL,17,Ffunding for the Department of Health
OL,18,Fand Social Care to address additional
OL,19,Fcosts incurred by Manx Care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
