PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779304271
OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,FA former advisor to the UK Government,
OL,7,FProfessor Reid has combined her
OL,8,Fclinical work with a number of senior
OL,9,Facademic and leadership positions,
OL,10,Fincluding national Executive Medical
OL,11,FDirector, Director of Education &
OL,12,FQuality and interim Chief Executive
OL,13,Ffor Health Education England, as a
OL,14,FDean of Postgraduate Medicine at
OL,15,FLondon Deanery and Vice President of
OL,16,Fthe Royal College of Obstetricians &
OL,17,FGynaecologists.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
