CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779304271
OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,FHon. Claire Christian MHK, Minister
OL,7,Ffor Health and Social Care added: "I
OL,8,Fwould like to thank Professor Reid for
OL,9,Fher leadership and service in the
OL,10,Fpivotal role of Chair of Manx Care.
OL,12,F"Her extensive experience and
OL,13,Fknowledge has been felt across the
OL,14,Fwhole organisation and her commitment
OL,15,Fto improving standards has been
OL,16,Fevident throughout.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
