PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779304271
OL,3,CChair of Manx Care to step down as it
OL,4,Centers 'next phase' of leadership
OL,6,F"Her guidance and support for myself
OL,7,Fand colleagues during this period has
OL,8,Fbeen invaluable and I look forward to
OL,9,Fcontinuing to work with her over the
OL,10,Fcoming months as we conclude the
OL,11,FGovernance Review and take the
OL,12,Fappropriate steps to consider and
OL,13,Fappoint a new Chair."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
